Osceola Macarthy Adams https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Osceola_Macarthy_Adams 0 Osceola Macarthy Adams (June 13, 1890 – November 20, 1983) was an American actress, drama teacher, director, and clothing designer. She was one of the 22 founders of the Delta Sigma Theta sorority.
